_sText:
a keypad that makes either fire lasers an exploding barrel or a trigger hurt

instructions.
press big white button
press one of the small buttons
press big white button again
press a different small one
press big white button again
press a different small one
press big white button again
press a different small one

the 1st small white button makes fire
the 2nd small white button makes lasers
the 3rd small white button makes a trigger_hurt behind the spawn point
the 4th small white button spawns a exploding_barrel
